OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Joe Randall
OL,5,FJoe Randall, Age 100, RAF
OL,7,FInterviewed 21 November 2023
OL,9,FA member of 5022 Airfield Construction
OL,10,FSquadron, Joe Randall arrived in
OL,11,FFrance shortly after D-Day, tasked
OL,12,Fwith building an airstrip from scratch
OL,13,Fin fields near Caen.
OL,15,FThis was so that RAF planes could
OL,16,Fsupport the Army's advance in the
OL,17,Fearly weeks without having to fly
OL,18,Flonger distances from UK airfields.
