OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Joe Randall
OL,5,FMr Randall had trained in Scotland to
OL,6,Fconstruct airfields before crossing
OL,7,Ffrom Portsmouth at the end of June and
OL,8,Flanding on Juno beach.
OL,10,FHe said: "We came over on one of those
OL,11,FYankee ships, the bigger one because
OL,12,Fof our equipment. We had to have time
OL,13,Fto get the land, it wasn't just a
OL,14,Fhundred yards long.
OL,16,F"We couldn't get to our job because
OL,17,Fthe land hadn't been taken.
OL,19,F"What we did within in a couple of
OL,20,Fhours of being there we had to go into
OL,21,Fthese woods.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
