OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Joe Randall
OL,5,F"Because our infantry when they are on
OL,6,Fthe move any troops in the woods they
OL,7,Fwere left there, they didn't bother
OL,8,Fwith that. And that was our first job,
OL,9,Fto clear that one.
OL,11,F"It was not a big hero job but there
OL,12,Fwere a few bullets flying around. It
OL,13,Fwasn't that bad. They gave in and that
OL,14,Fwas it."
OL,16,FAfter this skirmish the squadron
OL,17,Fmembers found the designated site,
OL,18,Flevelled the land, laid track and made
OL,19,Fthe site operational in about eight
OL,20,Fdays.
