OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Joe Randall
OL,5,F"I was a Corporal, but we were a
OL,6,Fpretty good bunch I think."
OL,8,FAmong the planes using the airfield
OL,9,Fwere Hawker Typhoons that had been
OL,10,Fadapted to carry bombs.
OL,12,FThey attacked gun batteries and German
OL,13,FE-Boats and helped dislodge enemy
OL,14,Ftroops who were digging in.
