OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Joe Randall
OL,5,FMr Randall said: "Our Tiffys (Hawker
OL,6,FTyphoons) went up to the front line
OL,7,Fwhich was just over the road. We saw
OL,8,Fthem taking off and then sometimes go
OL,9,Fdown in action. They did some
OL,10,Fmagnificent work those pilots. They
OL,11,Fwere friendly.
OL,13,F"We would be there in the morning to
OL,14,Fsee them off and they always gave us a
OL,15,Fwave."
